22
00:01:26,639 --> 00:01:27,879
Our efforts aren't in vain.

23
00:01:30,558 --> 00:01:31,558
No.

24
00:01:31,999 --> 00:01:32,999
This can't happen.

25
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:35,079
This can't happen.

26
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:36,239
Why shouldn't it?

27
00:01:36,719 --> 00:01:38,118
Your Dantian can be restored.

28
00:01:38,519 --> 00:01:39,519
Aren't you happy?

29
00:01:40,038 --> 00:01:42,359
(Only people in love
can activate the Love Flower toxin.)

30
00:01:43,239 --> 00:01:45,318
(But if they get pierced,)

31
00:01:46,118 --> 00:01:47,599
(they will be poisoned by it.)

32
00:01:48,439 --> 00:01:49,838
(Once moved for each other,)

33
00:01:50,678 --> 00:01:52,558
(they will suffer agonizing pain.)

34
00:01:56,359 --> 00:01:57,359
What's wrong, Feiyang?

35
00:01:58,318 --> 00:01:58,959
I'm fine.

36
00:01:59,278 --> 00:02:00,799
But you're coughing up blood!

37
00:02:00,999 --> 00:02:01,678
- Let me...
- You!

38
00:02:01,678 --> 00:02:02,368
So annoying!

39
00:02:03,558 --> 00:02:05,038
Always rushing to do things for me,

40
00:02:05,038 --> 00:02:06,038
