42
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:09,999
I, Zhao Feiyang, have great power.

43
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:12,478
I don't need your help!

44
00:02:13,998 --> 00:02:15,239
Don't come to Zhao family.

45
00:02:15,239 --> 00:02:18,878
♪The Stone of Three Lifetimes
reveals your past♪

46
00:02:18,878 --> 00:02:20,192
