47
00:02:20,878 --> 00:02:21,878
Zhao Feiyang.

48
00:02:23,598 --> 00:02:24,598
You...

49
00:02:24,998 --> 00:02:25,998
Say it again.

50
00:02:28,519 --> 00:02:29,838
