the other is me♪

63
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:28,759
I'm sorry.

64
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:30,479
Xiao Ran.

65
00:03:32,118 --> 00:03:34,158
I don't want you
to suffer this pain too.

66
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:37,039
